Class MusicGUI

public class MusicGUI
extends javafx.application.Application
implements MusicSubject, MusicObserver
MusicGUI class is a ConcreteObserver and a ConcreteSubject. Notified by its subject of any requests made and notifies its observer the results of the request It is a different experience to access the MMLS application.
